<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Leon) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうだった？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's going on?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あいつめ、ようやく白状したぞ。
やはり食べ物をとってこさせたのは
孤児院の子ども達の為だったらしい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That asshole finally confessed.
Apparently she had me get that food
for the sake of the orphanage children.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それどころか
実際は人質などとっていなかったようだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In fact, it would seem she didn't
even actually take any hostages.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ、あいつもいいとこあるじゃないか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well look at that, she's got
some good qualities after all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そのようだな。　ところでスタン……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It seems so. By the way, Stahn...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ん？　どうした？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hm? What's up?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕がもうお前を許したと思っているのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you actually think I've forgiven you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>えぇぇ！？　許してくれてないの！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huuuh?! You haven't forgiven me?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>当たり前だ！
食欲に負けて僕を裏切るとは
友として恥ずかしいぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course not! I'm embarrassed to be
the friend of someone who gave into
his apetite and betrayed me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はは、ごめんごめん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haha, sorry, sorry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいから、さっさと自分の食べた
食料をもう一度とってこい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whatever, just hurry up and go get
more of the food you ate on me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかったよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>The voice acing doesn't match the expression, so I'm a little unsure what to do with this one as far as English wording LOL.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
